  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: c72c9706ba29a9d428084a4a0a43db7f, type: 3}
  m_Name: Path_2_aftermath_dialogue
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::DialogueObject
  dialogue:
  - "Now all that is left is to wait for the plans and investigation to come to effect.\n\nLet\u2019s
    wait a while and see what they manage to do."
  - '...


    ...


    ...'
  - 'Advisor! The sewer situation has been resolved.


    Rivera just reported in.
    The toxic spill cleanup was successful! However, the perpetrator was not identified.
    They have gotten away with what they did for now, and could do something similar
    again in the future.'
  - "<b>Water resources ++:</b>\nThe toxic waste\u2019s spread was halted before
    it could cause major damage.\n\n<b>Education +:</b>\nThe cleanup made for good
    news and practice on how to handle major problems quickly.\n\n<b>Disaster management
    --:</b>\nThe culprit got away with their irresponsible actions and may do this
    again."
